====== H8034: שֵׁם ======

===== Source =====

a primitive word [perhaps rather from  H7760  through the idea of definite and conspicuous  ; compare  H8064 ];

===== Meaning =====

position an  appellation , as a mark or memorial of individuality; by implication  honor ,  authority ,  character

===== Definitions =====

  - position
  - appellation
  - honor
  - authority
  - character

===== Usage =====

  base, (in-) fame(-ous), named(-d), renown, report.
